    FtcRevBlinkin

    public abstract class TrcRevBlinkin
extends TrcPriorityIndicator<TrcRevBlinkin.LEDPattern>
    This class implements a platform independent REV Blinkin device. This class is intended to be extended by a platform dependent device class which provides the abstract methods required by this class.
